Pakeha-Maori
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(formerly) a European living as a Maori.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: in recent years used in a pejorative sense for 'bone people' q.v.
